# Direct runtime dependencies for the Axiom Firewall container.
#
# This file is the source-of-truth for `pip-compile`; the resolved
# transitive closure is locked in `requirements.txt` in this same
# directory and consumed by deploy/firewall/Dockerfile.
#
# To refresh after bumping a pin or adding a dep:
#   pip-compile --generate-hashes deploy/firewall/requirements.in \
#               -o deploy/firewall/requirements.txt
#
# Dependabot watches both this file and the lock file (see
# .github/dependabot.yml).
#
# Stripe is optional — only required when STRIPE_SECRET_KEY is set —
# but pinned here so the prod image is identical regardless of who
# enables billing.

